message: A bit removed from the city, but they have a great rate (about 109 a night) and parking is free in case you want to rent a ride
Any hints? We ll stay for 2 weeks but I cannot find any great offer at AirBnB for two weeks
I also considered a couple other options in Tiburon and Sausalito, but the rates are not great and the Golden Gate fare kills you
also try http://www.9flats.com - might be cheaper
